# Exercise 005 - Exposing your application

1) As developer, deploy again your mysql application into the project
   "new-mysql", this time without removing the Service part;

2) Verify if the DeploymentConfig, Pods and Service are up&running

3) Check if mysql is reachable (either with just a netcat) from inside and
   outside the OpenShift Cluster;

4) Delete the service;

5) Create a new NodePort service, mapping port 30000;

6) Verify the status and the service object;

7) Verify the Service yaml;

8) Check if mysql is reachable (either with just a netcat) from inside and
   outside the OpenShift Cluster;
